MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: GRAARRGH! GRAARRGH! GRAAAARRRGH!
Khajuraho had somehow brought Jeran back to her senses, she swung her huge axe with all of her might to chop up Ω God.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: How dare you control Jeran like a raging circus beast dah～! Will never forgive you dah～, Jeran is the proudest and strongest tiger that no one can control dah～!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'GAAAAAH! IT HURTS IT HURTS IT HURTS!'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Of course it hurts dah～! You should feel the hurt dah～! GAAARRGH!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'Halt right there! Why art thy angry? Weren't thy happy earlier!? Girls should make love to girls, that's the happy end!'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You cannot decide what makes Jeran happy dah～! Jeran is a proud tiger dah～, not a domestic animal who is happy to be fed dah～!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'GAAAAGH!?'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Woah, she's running around and swinging his axe at such a speed that my eyes can't keep up. That tiger thing has the bites to match her bark.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Y-Yeah. Her fighting style is a bit savage, like a wild beast, however Miss Jeran is a more experienced fighter than us.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: She must be used to dealing with monsters.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Hmph. Whatever, as long as she defeats the Ω God. I was firing too much and was about to run out of ammunition.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: ? What's the matter, you? What's wrong, even if I don't care - were you injured by a stray bullet?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Eh? N-no, just that Yours Truly still hardly did anything at all! Might as well redeem myself here then, and cooperate with Jeran and defeat the enemy spectacularly! Ooh～Ho-ho-ho☆

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You sound like you're in blues... Haha, you're lonely because lil' Ranran let you go after hugging you like crazy just now, is that it?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You're thirsty to need someone to embrace you to make your body tingle... How naughty♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: W-Wrong! Don't sexually harass me! Even if it's true that cuddling with Jeran was so warm, it made Yours Truly forgot about the cold!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That's why Yours Truly's kind of sad that Jeran ran away the moment Ω God's grip on me was broken... Miss Jeran, just now she was telling me that she loved me, and hugging me a lot.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: But it's likely that was just Ω God making her say that. Thinking things like that now makes me dreary. Felt like we finally got over our previous schism and warmed up to each other.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: In Jeran's eyes, Yours Truly is just a 'bully' who hurt her terribly once upon a time--

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Gaaarrgh! It was nice to see unusually shy Sentosa accepting Jeran's 'love' though!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Sentosa usually looks sad whenever she talks to Jeran - Felt like she was keeping her distance even though Jeran wanted to be friends with her, it was so lonely!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Was happy to get along with her normally just now! But this is a different story dah～, what you should receive is not a thank you, but an axe dah～!!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Jeran is strong and powerful, so it doesn't matter what you do! But Sentosa is a girl who hates someone controlling her like cattle dah～!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You did a terrible thing to her, to Jeran's friend dah...! That's why Jeran is very angry dah～! GAAARRGH!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: ...That girl really.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Ahaha. You girls could be really good friends.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You two are very similar. You both think the other hates you, but you really love each other more than anyone else--

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You won't meet girls like that very often, so cherish them. This is my personal, unusually non-sexual advice to you.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Hmph.... Even I'm jealous of you girls.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Of course, I'm fine enough with just my mama and papa loving me. You girls however have other important people in your life besides your family, so why do you look so gloomy? Is there something troubling you?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Nothing.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Heh. Not a single thing bothers me, nothing.

Sentosa took out her sparklingly decorated artifact and began her incantations. The celebrity lady, loved and pampered like a precious flower, smiled contentedly - As if she has been given something she wants for the first time.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Miss Jeran! I'll cover you, just keep going and finish off Ω God!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Ω God? What's that? Is it this big monster?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Gauugh～! At least learn who your enemies are and think before you act oi! You're always like that, really can't leave you alone ah...!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Hu-huh? What? Why does Sentosa always get more and more grumpy when she talks to Jeran dah～!?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Does this look like a grumpy face? Stupid kid!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'Damn thy all damn thy all--! Damn! Wrong! This is wrong, this is not mine wants!'
The bullet-riddled, axed, sorcery-wounded Ω God cursed away.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'Don't be satisfied with just friendship! Love is thy true path!'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I'm convinced after what you've just said just now, that you're an absolute dumbass.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yeah. Do you really think these girls don't love each other?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'Ugh, ugh! UUUUGAAAH～!'
Hearing the victorious declarations of Asahikawa's group, Ω God was probably taken aback, retreated - and crawled furiously on the ground.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: ...So it ran away because it doesn't think you have a chance to win?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Not true! Look, look where Ω God's going...!
Ω God Captained towards the huge wall that divided this land in two. The Ω God then proceeded to smash it with tremendous force.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'Mine gospel art right! I am not wrong! I am God...! Thy ignorant and foolish humans art just blind to the truth of this world yet!'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'I was trying to teach thy, thy wretches, what is righteous love! Why can't thy understand? Fools! Fools! Ignorant animals without intelligence or reason...!'
Ω God slammed into the wall even harder, causing countless cracks to run through it. Soon after, the wall collapsed without a second thought--

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'HWAHAHAHAHA!'
Rolling over and running to the other side of the wall, Ω God laughed loudly. The landscape around it is armed, rugged, and slum-like, unlike Sheep City.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That must be the Wolf City - the area where only men live.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: It's just like what Pochy said, it's a really dirty little place.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Really? It doesn't really feel messy and it's more natural, Jeran likes here better than Sheep City dah～♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I bet you do. Aiyoh... Really wish you cared more about how you look, because we're both Flamarinian beastkin, and you're making Yours Truly status lower and makes me really paiseh, you know!?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Don't worry, if Jeran lowers it, Sentosa will raise it!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Muh, muuugh...!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Come now come now, let's stop flirting and get to work, shall we?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: W-We're not flirting! But - yeah, we haven't defeated the root of all evil, the Ω God, yet, have we? We can't afford to be complacent!
Yes, you're right. Let's quickly defeat the Ω God and get back to our original mission. Everybody, let's work together and keep our spirits up until the end.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Roger, Papa♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'HWAHAHA! Beat me? Me? Dream on! Thy fools who do not know true love can never defeat me!'
Just as Ω God bellowed, the ground around it rose. The earth was split open and a great number of tentacles overflowed from its depths.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Hmm. It seems that Ω God had also divided and placed its other half in male realm - the Wolf City. In this way, it divided itself into two and ruled each town.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: So it has now restored its formerly separated half in this way.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: So what if it restores itself?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'This is what happens--!'
Ω God intertwined with the tentacles that erupt from the depths of the earth and absorbed them. The two separated bodies fused together and become an even more gigantic monster.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'HWAHAHAHA! Scared now, foolish humans!? None can harm me, now that mine assembled myself and become the one and only perfect God!'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Ω God
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: 'Despair, and prostrate thyselves before the Ω God! HAHAHAHAHAHA!'

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Seems like I have to repeat myself again. I am not listening to your garbage.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I myself am the only master I have.
Muttering this to herself, Asahikawa raised her gun, and everyone else stepped forward to follow suit.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That's right. There are countless kinds of love in this world and it should be up to the individual to choose what kind of love he or she wants.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yet Ω God can only recognised and enforced one kind of love, who is too narrow-minded to call itself a preacher of love.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Gaaarrrrrgh! Not sure what's going on, but we will defeat the enemy dah～! It might be difficult to do it alone, so we have to do it together dah～!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Haiyoh, why are you so savage... It's ok though, Miss Jeran is always right in what she says.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You all--
Asahikawa looked at her friends standing alongside her in surprise. Her face confused, as if she had accidentally put something nasty in her mouth, before gripping her gun even tighter.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: -Whatever, okay. I'm the great, kawaii, supreme Queen, so I won't complain about every single thing my underlings do.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: (Mama... I love you, but I hate you too, for leaving me there, sleeping at the bottom of the ice.)

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: (However. Now I feel like my hatred of you is gone and only love remains.)

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: (It's strange. I'm starting to think that it was a good thing that you abandoned me, Mama. Because I met people who accepts me in outside world. I found all kinds of fun and happy things.)

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: (Don't think of me thinking like that as my betrayal to you, Mama.)
And so the final battle began.
